GIT Prompt for BASH

    Picture worth a thousand words, see wiki for screenshots


DEPENDECY
    bash (tested with v3.2.33) 
    git  (optinal)
    svn  (optinal)
    sed
    tput (terminfo)
    tty
    grep 
    locale
    id 


